Oauth implementation we required 4 key things
1)user
2)Application  --  like productservice or payment service
3)



for example i implement one server like userserver
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-oauth2-authorization-server</artifactId>
</dependency>

i am keep this dependency in userservice pom.xml file now userservice is act like a authorization server